				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Escape The Grimm Wish" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>What stories we believe were fairy tales might indeed be real after all&amp;hellip;  We received word of a change to history right in the heart of Germany&amp;rsquo;s Black Forest and it appears to be something right out of the pages of a storybook.  You always had a Grimm Wish&amp;hellip; to have your own happily ever after&amp;hellip; but it appears that comes at a cost.  The woods are filled with wonders.  A talking frog begs for a kiss and a tower with hair dangling below waits for you, but there also is danger.  The big, bad wolf stalks you from the shadows, while clever witches tempt you with sweets.  If you are to survive these woods, you might need to brush up on your fairy tales and avoid straying too far from the path.  After all, this Grimm Wish might not be everything you thought it would be&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;About Escape the Crate escape room boxes:&amp;#10;Each box has over a dozen unique puzzles which all fit the theme. Every item in the box has a purpose and will help you escape in time. Clue are hidden everywhere and in this game you need to think inside the box. Each box is a complete story.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;These missions can be challenging and it is very possible you won't escape before the time limit. You can always reset the game using our instructions or you can continue playing past the time limit to see the mission to completion.&amp;#10;Every challenge you will face will have a set of hints, which you can choose to reveal when your team needs them. If you are completely stumped, even after the hints, the solution is also provided.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note: You will need a fully charged computer or mobile device to play this escape room.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
